4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential technologies like JavaScript and Python. This 18-week program includes three classes each week and maintains a teacher-student ratio of 1:7. Participants will learn to build websites, work with front-end libraries, and utilize APIs. No prior coding skills are required, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. Upon completion, students receive a certification as a Full-Stack Developer. The program culminates in a hands-on project that showcases their skills and enhances job readiness. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop